enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve adding custom data from a file path or URL, requiring similar input validation and processing.
Both methods update the internal state of the FakeValuesService by adding or updating locale-specific data.
After adding a URL, the method fetchObject can be used to retrieve the newly added data, ensuring the data is correctly loaded and accessible.
Similar to fetchObject, fetch can be used to retrieve specific data points from the newly added URL, validating the data integration.
